<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Grant Approved - MaalEdu</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            color: #374151;
        }

        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981, #059669);
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .coupon-box {
            background-color: #ecfdf5;
            border: 2px solid #10b981;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .coupon-code {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #10b981;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .footer p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #10b981;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>ðŸŽ‰ Congratulations!</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>Your Grant Application Has Been Approved!</h2>
            <p>Hi <%= userName %>,</p>

            <p>We're excited to inform you that your grant application for <strong>
                    <%= courseTitle %>
                </strong> has been
                approved!</p>

            <div class="coupon-box">
                <p style="margin: 0; color: #10b981; font-weight: bold;">Your 100% Discount Coupon:</p>
                <div class="coupon-code">
                    <%= couponCode %>
                </div>
                <p style="margin: 0; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">Use this code at checkout on maaledu.com</p>
            </div>

            <h3>How to Use Your Coupon:</h3>
            <ol style="color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">
                <li>Visit <a href="https://maaledu.com/courses" style="color: #10b981;">maaledu.com/courses</a></li>
                <li>Find your approved course: <strong>
                        <%= courseTitle %>
                    </strong></li>
                <li>Click "Buy Now" or "Enroll"</li>
                <li>Enter coupon code <strong>
                        <%= couponCode %>
                    </strong> at checkout</li>
                <li>Complete enrollment with 100% discount!</li>
            </ol>

            <p>You can now enroll in your course completely free! The coupon will give you full access to the course
                content on our learning platform.</p>

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="https://maaledu.com/courses" class="btn">Start Learning Now â†’</a>
            </div>

            <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">
                <strong>Note:</strong> This coupon is valid for the specific course mentioned in your grant application.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Congratulations and welcome to the MaalEdu community!<br>The MaalEdu Team</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 10px;">
                <a href="https://maaledu.com" style="color: #10b981;">maaledu.com</a> |
                <a href="mailto:support@maaledu.com" style="color: #10b981;">support@maaledu.com</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>